  <div class="subfield">
    <strong>$l - Library of Congress call number</strong>

    <div class="description">
      LC series call number when it is given as part of the
      series statement.
    </div>

    <div class="description2 description">
      Occurs when an item is issued as part of a series during a
      period of time and has been classified under the Library of
      Congress call number of that series for that period. The
      call number is assigned using the <em>Library of Congress
      Classification</em> or <em>LC Classification-Additions and
      Change</em>; two publications that are maintained by the
      Library of Congress.
    </div>

    <div class="example">
      <table width="100%">
