  <div class="subfield">
    <strong>$v - Volume/sequential designation</strong>

    <div class="description">
      Volume number or other sequential designation used in a
      series statement. Alternate numbering systems, preceded by
      an equal sign (=), are not placed in separate subfields.
    </div>

