  <div class="subfield">
    <strong>$x - International Standard Serial Number</strong>

    <div class="description">
      International Standard Serial Number (ISSN) for a series
      title given in a series statement. The ISSN is an
      authoritative-agency data element. ISSNs are assigned to
      serial publications (including series) by national centers
      under the auspices of the ISSN Network.
    </div>

